{"tid":1785625,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"須防大意失荊州 - 古德明","createTime":"2019-12-16T13:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T13:52:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"83362cbea04c3c69bf697034bacd24e0f920ffcb","tid":1785625,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:49:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191216/20825684/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191216%2F20825684%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7lFFw%2Fpr%2F0Xu32W9HouEUHQ%3D&h=f9a68e32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191216%2F20825684%2F&h=43f3f528\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191216/20825684/</a><br />\n<br />\n須防大意失荊州 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191216/large/1576396214_6842.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191216%2Flarge%2F1576396214_6842.jpg&h=f53daa04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十二月初，人權組織CIVICUS發表亞洲各地自由指數，以臺灣居首，日本、南韓次之。臺灣這個第一，未必值得恭維。<br />\n<br />\n今日德國民主自由，但其民主是自衛式民主（defensive democracy），一些「自由」必須限制，如禁用納粹黨與共產黨的徽章、符號等。雖然納粹黨與德國共產黨之禍都已成歷史，但德國人懂得懲前毖後。<br />\n<br />\n中華民國國民黨政府七十年前播遷臺灣，風雨飄搖，不能不頒布《臺灣省戒嚴令》，穩住局勢，實行黨禁，共產黨不能越臺海雷池半步。當時臺灣固然不民主，但無愧「自由中國」稱號。今日論者多以那自衛式自由詬病蔣介石，殊不知一些自由是限制了，大躍進、文革等浩劫卻避過了。蔣經國一九八七年解除戒嚴令，但堅決「不與中共政權交涉」，中共仍然滲透無從，直到二零零八年馬英九主政。<br />\n<br />\n馬英九率領國民黨向中共靠攏，從此中共紅旗肆無忌憚飄揚臺灣街頭，中共幹部更是升堂入室。國民黨現在簡直變成中共附庸，其來屆總統候選人韓國瑜去年十二月才出任高雄市長，今年三月即赴大陸朝聖。要是在當年，這樣一個黨早就給蔣介石禁了，而我不會認為這是不民主、不自由。畢竟中共之惡，浮於納粹黨；中共對民主自由之威脅，更未如納粹黨般灰飛煙滅。今日臺灣的民進黨政府切勿大意失荊州。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"49fe08d9c549a304f3cc98b0a98f63803e71a345","tid":1785625,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pie4mpm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPie4mpm.jpg&h=4cc5750a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-2.xx&amp;oh=f485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a&amp;oe=5EAED219\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sin2-2.xx%26oh%3Df485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a%26oe%3D5EAED219&h=70a59658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}